# Generated artifacts must stay byte-identical across platforms (the freshness
# gates in validate.yml diff them against a freshly-regenerated copy). Pin them
# to LF so a Windows checkout (core.autocrlf=true) can't silently rewrite them
# to CRLF and flake the `git diff --exit-code` / `--check` freshness steps.
generated/tools.json text eol=lf
commander/TOOLS.md text eol=lf
commander/TOOLS.mcp.md text eol=lf
